<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Piece from the lower part of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">base</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.30</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.11</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.85</measure>). Nothing interpretable survives above; there is a left edge, but the lay-out suggests that this is a section from a composite monument.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>
<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure>-<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.021</measure>; not very well-cut</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>?<date notBefore="0201" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Third century A.D.</date>
 (lettering)</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
